description: The CDU suffers its worst-ever poll result in the city state, as the left consolidates power.
title: Hamburg election: Merkel party 'slumps as Greens surge'
title_page: Hamburg election: Merkel party 'slumps as Greens surge' - BBC News
maintext: "We have a very challenging situation for democracy in Germany, and the CDU is tied up in its own problems... It will be up to us to give the land direction and trust," Mr Habeck said.
